1. No spam or self-promotion (server invites, advertisements, etc) without permission from a staff member. This includes DMing fellow members.
2. No age-restricted or obscene content. This includes text, images, or links featuring nudity, sex, hard violence, or other graphically disturbing content.
3. Treat everyone with respect. Absolutely no harassment, witch hunting, sexism, racism, or hate speech will be tolerated.
4. Mild Swears are fine
5. If you see something against the rules or something that makes you feel unsafe, let staff know. We want this server to be a welcoming space!